                <div class="mr-3"><img src="img/icon_privacy.svg" alt="Privacy"></div>
                <div>
                    <h5 class="mb-2"><%- gettext("Total Privacy") %></h5>
                    <p class="mb-0"><%- gettext("Private Internet Access never keeps any records of users' online activities. You can rest assured knowing you have complete privacy, and nobody knows what you're doing online.") %></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-46 d-flex mb-5">
