            <p class="quotes_text"><b><q><%- gettext("Our readers made it abundantly clear that Private Internet Access should be your first stop for protecting your private browsing data.") %></q></b></p>
            <hr>
            <img src="img/logo_lifehacker_bar.png" alt="lifehacker" class="lifehacker">
            <img src="img/qoutemarks.svg" alt="quotes" class="quotes">
